    "body": "This happens when a on_read callback happens concurrently with shutdown in two threads.\r\n\r\nT1 calls set_ready on fd and schedule the closure, set CLOSURE_NOT_READY\r\nT2 shuts down fd, does not thing on CLOSURE_NOT_READY\r\nT1 calls accept4 on the fd, which will return EINVAL\r\n"
